<P>In the Tables, page 2, for Scolopax candida. (Plover.) read Tringa Squatarola? Grey Sandpiper? (Plover.) page 3, for Golden-Crowned Tru&s;h, read Golden-Crowned Thru&s;h.</P>
<P>In Appendix I, page 16, under the head of Hirundo purpurea, for, when it &s;uppo&s;ed, &amp;c. read, when it is &s;uppo&s;ed, &amp;c.</P>
</DIV1>
