<CELL>The Glow-Worm (Lampyris noctiluca? the fe|male) begins to &s;parkle in the gra&s;s, in humid &s;ituations, during the evenings.</CELL>
</ROW>
<ROW>
<CELL>Turdus minor (G.)</CELL>
<CELL>Wood-Thru&s;h. Little Thru&s;h.</CELL>
<CELL>&nbsp;</CELL>
