<L>Ia<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="3 letters">&s;i mon<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="3 letters"> Ip&s;s jam carmuna rupes,</L>
<L>Ip&s;a &s;onant arbu&s;ta."</L>
<BIBL><HI>VIRGIL.</HI></BIBL></Q></CELL>
